class=\"\"><strong>WHEN THE EMBERS GLOW</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\"><strong>All Day Dining </strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\"><strong>7 Days • 11am-Late<br></strong>Open every day except Christmas Day</p></div>\n3647:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\"><strong>FIND US</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\"><strong>The Terrace, Level 4</strong> <br>The Star Brisbane<br><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--white\">Ph. </span><a href=\"tel:+61721116869\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--white\">(07) 2111 6869</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\"><a href=\"/careers\"><strong>Careers</strong></a><strong><br></strong><a href=\"https://www.tassisgroup.com.au/business-opportunities\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Business Opportunities</strong></a></p></div>\n3731:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\">🅿 Free validated parking for diners.</p></div>\n3869:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-small\">10% Weekend surcharge (20% on Public Holidays). Card payment surcharge applies.</p></div>\n3953:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\">Branding and design by <a href=\"https://www.allocreative.com.au\">Allo Creative</a></p></div>\n4049:    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" version=\"1.1\" style=\"display:none\" data-usage=\"social-icons-svg\"><symbol id=\"instagram-unauth-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\"><path d=\"M46.91,25.816c-0.073-1.597-0.326-2.687-0.697-3.641c-0.383-0.986-0.896-1.823-1.73-2.657c-0.834-0.834-1.67-1.347-2.657-1.73c-0.954-0.371-