22&quot;,&quot;collectionId&quot;:&quot;68ec80c41a3cb06a39c2f522&quot;,&quot;design&quot;:&quot;slideshow&quot;,&quot;autoplay&quot;:true,&quot;controls&quot;:false,&quot;thumbnails&quot;:false,&quot;methodOption&quot;:&quot;transient&quot;,&quot;autoplay-duration&quot;:3,&quot;auto-crop&quot;:true,&quot;square-thumbs&quot;:true,&quot;show-meta-basic&quot;:true,&quot;show-meta&quot;:false,&quot;show-meta-only-title&quot;:false&#125;\" data-block-type=\"8\" data-sqsp-block=\"gallery\" id=\"block-a7ea98e7a4c0bf5735e4\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:2494:      href=\"https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/darkshepherd/reservations/create/search?venues=darkshepherd,pompetteau,yamasgreekdrink,stilts,richandrarerestaurant,fatcowrestaurant,longwangchopstickhouse,opabarmezze,massimorestaurantandbar,foshbarrestaurant\" \n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:2515:      href=\"https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/darkshepherd/reservations/create/search?venues=darkshepherd,pompetteau,yamasgreekdrink,stilts,richandrarerestaurant,fatcowrestaurant,longwangchopstickhouse,opabarmezze,massimorestaurantandbar,foshbarrestaurant\" \n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:2641:  data-src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/31c115a6-e827-44d6-a761-76de938364a7/DSH1_DS_Logo_Submark_White.png\"\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:2642:  data-image=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/31c115a6-e827-44d6-a761-76de938364a7/DSH1_DS_Logo_Submark_White.png\"\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:2648:  data-load=\"false\" elementtiming=\"system-image-block\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/31c115a6-e827-44d6-a761-76de938364a7/DSH1_DS_Logo_Submark_White.png\" width=\"629\" height=\"919\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 16.666666666666664vw\" style=\"display:block;object-position: var(--image-component-focal-point);object-fit: var(--image-component-object-fit);\" srcset=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/31c115a6-e827-44d6-a761-76de938364a7/DSH1_DS_Logo_Submark_White.png?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/31c115a6-e827-44d6-a761-76de938364a7/DSH1_DS_Logo_Submark_White.png?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/31c115a6-e827-44d6-a761-76de938364a7/DSH1_DS_Logo_Submark_White.png?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/31c115a6-e827-44d6-a761-76de938364a7/DSH1_DS_Logo_Submark_White.png?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/31c115a6-e827-44d6-a761-76de938364a7/DSH1_DS_Logo_Submark_White.png?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/31c115a6-e827-44d6-a761-76de938364a7/DSH1_DS_Logo_Submark_White.png?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/31c115a6-e827-44d6-a761-76de938364a7/DSH1_DS_Logo_Submark_White.png?format=2500w 2500w\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-loader=\"sqs\">\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:3092:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><h2 style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\">The flock gathers.</h2><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\">By night, the embers smoulder, lamb surrenders, and flavours rise like whispered secrets.<br>By day, the sun lends its warmth, casting light on Mediterranean marvels. Here, the dark and the bright find harmony. Lamb, revered as the heart of the feast, meets fire’s embrace.</p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\">The Marana Forni oven roars to life, transforming each bite into charred perfection. Far from ordinary, live seafood tanks meet a dry-aging lamb cabinet. It’s a myth waiting to unfold. A testament to provenance and passion.</p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\">Welcome to <em>Dark Shepherd</em>.<br>Born of fire. Bound by flavour.</p></div>\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:3109:  #block-395c53c3c348741c7cd5 .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:3152:          #block-395c53c3c348741c7cd5 .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:3176:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><div class=\"sqsrte-scaled-text-container\"><span class=\"sqsrte-scaled-text\"><h1 style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Mediterranean RESTAURANT AT THE STAR BRISBANE</h1></span></div></div>\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:3193:  #block-337fe9eecaab4be3a7b4 .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:3236:          #block-337fe9eecaab4be3a7b4 .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:3356:      Banquets\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:3377:      Banquets\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:4953:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">A bold awakening of Mediterranean flavours, succulent cuts, and a menu tailored for those who crave an unmatched intensity. White Pyrenees lamb, the wagyu of its kind, leads the flock, followed by an artistry of seafood and tender grilled meats, all baptised by fire. A timeless tradition, delivered with provenance and passion. Uncover the offerings.</p></div>\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:4970:  #block-28dc3c7facf5baafed41 .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:5013:          #block-28dc3c7facf5baafed41 .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:5037:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><div class=\"sqsrte-scaled-text-container\"><span class=\"sqsrte-scaled-text\"><h2 style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Fire, <strong>flavour</strong>, and flair.</h2></span></div></div>\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:5054:  #block-8e94e61bbe96ebd59212 .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:5097:          #block-8e94e61bbe96ebd59212 .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:5199:  data-src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb\"\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:5200:  data-image=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb\"\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:5206:  data-load=\"false\" elementtiming=\"system-image-block\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb\" width=\"1365\" height=\"2048\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"100vw\" style=\"display:block;object-position: var(--image-component-focal-point);object-fit: var(--image-component-object-fit);\" srcset=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb?format=2500w 2500w\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-loader=\"sqs\">\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:5779:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Craft an event that awakens a world of sensation. This is no mere gathering; it’s a rite of passage. An invitation to something beyond the ordinary.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Elect the 120-seat dining room for your revel, embellished with sandy beige booths and marble tables. Or, retreat into the private 10-seater, for those seeking a shadow of secrecy. Each corner of the space beckons with an intoxicating sense of possibility.</p></div>\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:5796:  #block-fc13b32a8156a9158fcc .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:5839:          #block-fc13b32a8156a9158fcc .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:5863:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><div class=\"sqsrte-scaled-text-container\"><span class=\"sqsrte-scaled-text\"><h2 style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Host boldly,</strong> dine brilliantly.</h2></span></div></div>\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:5880:  #block-e530b86df3f7f70b2d97 .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:5923:          #block-e530b86df3f7f70b2d97 .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:6605:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Every glass tells a tale. Signature cocktails twist the classics with bold precision, while a 140-bottle wine list whispers of depth and intrigue. Premium spirits and perfectly chilled beers complete the arsenal. Raise your glass, and let the experience unfold—dark, daring, and unforgettable.</p></div>\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:6622:  #block-66e0e3d8814be2fbb96f .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:6665:          #block-66e0e3d8814be2fbb96f .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:6689:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><div class=\"sqsrte-scaled-text-container\"><span class=\"sqsrte-scaled-text\"><h2 style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>shadows rise</strong>, and spirits floW.</h2></span></div></div>\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:6706:  #block-ecd7081834a65b6f0fe8 .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:6749:          #block-ecd7081834a65b6f0fe8 .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:7282:</style><div class=\"fluid-engine fe-6750feef78771d72dcf68f64\"><div class=\"fe-block fe-block-c7a0dd62daea3318e2a6\"><div class=\"sqs-block newsletter-block sqs-block-newsletter\" data-blend-mode=\"normal\" data-block-type=\"51\" data-border-radii=\"&#123;&quot;topLeft&quot;:&#123;&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0&#125;,&quot;topRight&quot;:&#123;&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0&#125;,&quot;bottomLeft&quot;:&#123;&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0&#125;,&quot;bottomRight&quot;:&#123;&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0&#125;&#125;\" id=\"block-c7a0dd62daea3318e2a6\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:7932:  data-src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/31c115a6-e827-44d6-a761-76de938364a7/DSH1_DS_Logo_Submark_White.png\"\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:7933:  data-image=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/31c115a6-e827-44d6-a761-76de938364a7/DSH1_DS_Logo_Submark_White.png\"\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:7939:  data-load=\"false\" elementtiming=\"system-image-block\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/31c115a6-e827-44d6-a761-76de938364a7/DSH1_DS_Logo_Submark_White.png\" width=\"629\" height=\"919\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 8.333333333333332vw\" style=\"display:block;object-position: var(--image-component-focal-point);object-fit: var(--image-component-object-fit);\" srcset=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/31c115a6-e827-44d6-a761-76de938364a7/DSH1_DS_Logo_Submark_White.png?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/31c