color--white\">(07) 2111 6869</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\"><a href=\"/careers\"><strong>Careers</strong></a><strong><br></strong><a href=\"https://www.tassisgroup.com.au/business-opportunities\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Business Opportunities</strong></a></p></div>\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:8111:  #block-6c1882ba256c1758c54a .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:8154:          #block-6c1882ba256c1758c54a .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:8178:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\">🅿 Free validated parking for diners.</p></div>\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:8195:  #block-7457c96877fe51b5b52c .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:8238:          #block-7457c96877fe51b5b52c .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:8300:                <use class=\"sqs-use--icon\" xlink:href=\"/universal/svg/social-accounts.svg#facebook-unauth-icon\"></use>\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:8301:                <use class=\"sqs-use--mask\" xlink:href=\"/universal/svg/social-accounts.svg#facebook-unauth-mask\"></use>\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:8316:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-small\">10% Weekend surcharge (20% on Public Holidays). Card payment surcharge applies.</p></div>\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:8333:  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1730853889851_67983 .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:8376:          #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1730853889851_67983 .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:8400:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\">Branding and design by <a href=\"https://www.allocreative.com.au\">Allo Creative</a></p></div>\n/tmp/darkshepherd-home.html:8417:  #block-36ee380f333ec318e23a .sqs-html-content {\n/tmp/d