data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"The concept structure will be: home as the cinematic entry, menu as a curated dining overview, functions as private dining/event enquiry, and contact as visit details. I’m keeping the live booking, gift voucher, Instagram/Facebook, phone, address, hours, surcharge, parking, and source menu intent intact."}

